Class UserProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.ualberta.CMPUT3012019T02.alexandria.model.user.UserProfile

  • public class UserProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    A model class for user details, which holds its username, full name email address, phone number, and picture if any, used to create an instance of a user and to pass information to activity classes
